<div class="mainbody">
  <div class="banner">
    <header>
      <div class="container headcontent">
        <div class="row d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="col-sm-3 logo">
            <%= image_tag asset_url("newlogo2_white.png") %>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-6 justify-content-center">
            <h1 class="headcontent">Welcome to FlexTables</h1>
            <p class="headcontent">The easy way to plan your Flex Classes</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container maincontent">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="textarea p-4">
            <h2 class="maincontent">What is FlexTables?</h2>
            <p class="maincontent">FlexTables is optimist for schools with "Lernbüro" System.</p>
            <br>
            <h2 class="maincontent">For Teachers:</h2>
            <p class="maincontent">Keep track of your student's flex classes, digitalise content and homework and keep track of attendance.</p>
            <br>
            <h2 class="maincontent">For Students:</h2>
            <p class="maincontent">Organise your flex classes and keep track of your homework.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <div class="textarea p-5">
            <header class="head-form">
              <h2 class="maincontent">Let's start</h2>
            </header>
            <br>

            <div class="field-set">
              <%= simple_form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
                <div class="form-inputs">
                  <%= f.input :email,
                              required: false,
                              autofocus: true,
                              input_html: { autocomplete: "email", class: "lg-input maincontent" },
                              label_html: { class: "lg-label maincontent" } %>
                  <%= f.input :password,
                              required: false,
                              input_html: { autocomplete: "current-password", class: "lg-input maincontent" },
                              label_html: { class: "lg-label maincontent" } %>
                  <%= f.input :remember_me, 
                              input_html: { class: "rem-input maincontent" },
                              label_html: { class: "rem-label maincontent" }, 
                              as: :boolean if devise_mapping.rememberable? %>
                </div>

                <div class="form-actions text-center">
                  <%= f.submit "Log in", class: "btn log-in" %>
                </div>
              <% end %>

              <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container ldp-content">
    <div class="line-wrapper">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
        <hr class="ldp-content w-25">
        <h2 class="ldp-content">About FlexTable System</h2>
        <hr class="ldp-content w-25">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="schoolsystem-banner">
    <h1 class="sb-text">Lernbüro</h1>
    <br>
    <h2 class="sb-text">Make teaching more individual</h2>
  </div>
    
  <div class="container ft-description">
    <div class="mt-4">
      <br>
      <br>
      <p class="ft-text">Das Lernarrangement Lernbüro bietet den Kindern die Möglichkeit, 
      Lernen als selbstverantwortlichen und selbst gesteu-erten Prozess zu begreifen. 
      Es ermöglicht einen hohen Grad an Differenzierung. 
      Jeder Schüler kann sein eigenes Lernvor-haben planen, durchführen und reflektierend abschließen.</p>
      <br>
      <br>
      <p class="ft-text">Das Lernarrangement Lernbüro bietet den Kindern die Möglichkeit, 
